{"tid":566931,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"BlackBerry OS 將於兩年後正式收皮！！","createTime":"2018-02-20T11:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T14:25:26.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"30eb338d6274d390afe1c302bc618c11b2d3f48d","tid":566931,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:20:46.000Z","msg":"BlackBerry 宣佈將會在 2 年後關閉 World 軟件商店，同時完全停止對 BlackBerry 系統的一切支援，在未來兩年亦只會提供必需的系統修正檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pixel.nymag.com/imgs/daily/intel/2012/07/10/10-rip-blackberry-rip.w710.h473.2x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpixel.nymag.com%2Fimgs%2Fdaily%2Fintel%2F2012%2F07%2F10%2F10-rip-blackberry-rip.w710.h473.2x.jpg&h=72f6c5f7&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/02/17/blackberry-os-world-close-in-2-years/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F02%2F17%2Fblackberry-os-world-close-in-2-years%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=%2Fd4RTiGqAtN9HQfMtucQBy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=735b369c\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/02/17/blackberry-os-world-close-in-2-years/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"cbe2c499d1fe6d7e69fa53745b305010f9d44d32","tid":566931,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:23:37.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/192248_8bf805d6bd542ed61550268b47487320.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F192248_8bf805d6bd542ed61550268b47487320.png&h=725195c8&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n已經停止生產手機的 BlackBerry，授權其他手機廠商生產和銷售手機，不過採用的系統則是 Android。BlackBerry 表明他們準備在兩年後全面使用 Android 平台，現時使用 BlackBerry OS 裝置的用戶只剩數百萬，如果在這段期間有大量 BlackBerry OS 的用戶需求，他們屆時才會考慮重新推出這系統的新產品，否則 BlackBerry OS 和 BlackBerry World 都會在兩年後徹底關閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"ed9896f0ba53a8b484fb2b6eb6dcff104ccae2fd","tid":566931,"uid":2819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:32:11.000Z","msg":"Berry 出keyboard 你話幾好呢"},{"pid":"6a16cdf4039e0667c45dbbb10215707331d9d5ae","tid":566931,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:34:23.000Z","msg":"Keyone 幾型仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1807650b5a5b31df468c76620f5c7c870b09ca3c","tid":566931,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a16cdf4039e0667c45dbbb10215707331d9d5ae","tid":566931,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:34:23.000Z","msg":"Keyone 幾型仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:40:29.000Z","msg":"Tcl生產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"788aaa5454d5ff4d4c51f7b32d7091ebfb6da00c","tid":566931,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T11:54:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5a8195518b77ea0b3acb9d5afd93602fa1de64","tid":566931,"uid":32585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:25:26.000Z","msg":"仲未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://crackberry.com/blackberry-announces-extended-support-blackberry-10-and-bbos-some-caveats\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcrackberry.com%2Fblackberry-announces-extended-support-blackberry-10-and-bbos-some-caveats&d=%2Fd4RTiGqAtN9HQfMtucQBy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=f00401eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://crackberry.com/blackberry-announces-extended-support-blackberry-10-and-bbos-some-caveats</a>"}]}